- TO WHERE? HONEY,

17:18.420 --> 17:20.249
TO THE ONE PLACE WHERE OUR
LOVE IS NOT FORBIDDEN,

17:20.250 --> 17:22.880
THE ONE PLACE WHERE
WE CAN TRULY BE FREE!

17:24.250 --> 17:25.289
CALABASAS.

17:25.290 --> 17:27.579
(angelic chorus)

17:27.580 --> 17:28.879
