17:28.880 --> 17:30.749
- YES!
- COME ON, WE GOTTA GO!

17:30.750 --> 17:32.289
- OH, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT!
- HONEY, PLEASE,

17:32.290 --> 17:33.669
