HAVE WINE THERE.

17:33.670 --> 17:37.039
NO! NO, NO, NO, I CAN'T
GO WITHOUT MY FAMILY.

17:37.040 --> 17:39.829
LENNOX, ZANDER, YOU
HAVE TO COME WITH US.

17:39.830 --> 17:42.829
