18:00.210 --> 18:02.579
YEAH. COME WITH US.

18:02.580 --> 18:04.169
BE WHO YOU REALLY ARE...

18:04.170 --> 18:06.289
IN CALABASAS.

18:06.290 --> 18:07.419
(angelic chorus)

18:07.420 --> 18:10.289
