18:37.330 --> 18:40.169
OH, LOOK, THERE IT IS!

18:40.170 --> 18:41.919
WE FOUND CALABASAS!

18:41.920 --> 18:44.379
(angelic chorus)

18:44.380 --> 18:48.209
Man: WHO GOES THERE?
STATE YOUR BUSINESS!

18:48.210 --> 18:52.120
IT'S US. WE WISH TO LIVE
FREELY HERE WITH THE REBELS.

18:53.250 --> 18:54.459
UNCLE JOE?

18:54.460 --> 18:56.749
MARCO!

18:56.750 --> 18:57.789
MARCO?

18:57.790 --> 18:59.540
