"SESQUIPEDALIAN."

19:27.710 --> 19:29.580
OH, MARCO.

19:31.000 --> 19:34.079
HEY, UH, LENNOX? YOU KNOW WE SHOULD
PROBABLY GET BACK TO TOLEDO.

19:34.080 --> 19:36.829
YOU KNOW, HAPPINESS CONTROL IS
JUST GONNA BE LOST WITHOUT YOU.

19:36.830 --> 19:37.879
LENNOX?

19:37.880 --> 19:40.289
OH GOD! LENNOX?

19:40.290 --> 19:41.830
