PILLS FOR NOTHING!

19:44.080 --> 19:46.539
SO, HERE WE ARE, SWEETIE.
TOGETHER FOREVER.

19:46.540 --> 19:47.709
WHERE DO YOU WANT TO LIVE?

19:47.710 --> 19:50.119
HMM, HOW ABOUT RIGHT
THERE BY THE RIVER?

19:50.120 --> 19:52.249
