THAT'S NOT GONNA BE GOOD.

19:52.250 --> 19:54.169
THERE'S GONNA BE FLOODING
AND MOSQUITOES DOWN THERE.

19:54.170 --> 19:55.879
HOW ABOUT THIS, WHY DON'T WE
LIVE UP HERE ON THE HILL,

19:55.880 --> 19:57.419
WHERE WE HAVE A NICE
VIEW OF THE RIVER?

19:57.420 --> 19:59.209
NO, BUT IF WE LIVE
UP ON THE HILL,

19:59.210 --> 20:01.999
